{"tid":338792,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"≪建軍大業≫討論區","createTime":"2017-07-28T13:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T16:53:27.000Z","uid":30768,"like":4,"dislike":183,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"595e018a4a338ecc8cfba57e03b88999900af8af","tid":338792,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"1927年的四一二反革命政變導致國共第一次合作破裂，大革命也從勝利走向失敗。在共產黨員、國民黨右派以及革命群眾被蔣介石為首的國民黨大肆屠殺期間，共產黨人總結了經驗教訓，決定獨立領導武裝鬥爭和創建革命隊伍。由周恩來、賀龍、葉挺、朱德等人在8月1日發起南昌起義，打響了武裝反抗國民黨反動派的第一槍。毛澤東和盧德銘也於9月9日在湖南東部和江西西部發動秋收起義。一幕幕波瀾壯闊的戰役和動人心魄的革命歷史也由此展開。<br />\n<br />\n內地尋日已經上咗映，但係香港要3號先睇得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。有冇巴打同我一樣特登上咗去睇嘅入黎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5bbd3df712621459f0a81c599d65a1ee1e8ff4","tid":338792,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"意大利都未統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7048fce76626eb6349595d4b41d596b48dc136e","tid":338792,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"意大利統一？"},{"pid":"2e56f1e51d9d7321075437f76c3735d3c8965ea5","tid":338792,"uid":4221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意大利都未統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b329ceac787dd83386eceebf65076f80c0e08c1","tid":338792,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"建軍個班元帥基本都不得好死"},{"pid":"29339cf235752529eb82f4f620e2a6782c0ad096","tid":338792,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0